      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the Distributed Node Consensus Protocol (DNCP), a generic state synchronization protocol that uses the Trickle algorithm and hash trees.  DNCP is an abstract protocol and must be combined with a specific profile to make a complete implementable protocol.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
